      • getHandleToSelectedCard

        public PersonCardHandle getHandleToSelectedCard​()
        Returns a handle to the selected PersonCardHandle. A maximum of 1 item can be selected at any time.
        Throws:
        java.lang.AssertionError - if no card is selected, or more than 1 card is selected.
        java.lang.IllegalStateException - if the selected card is currently not in the scene graph.
